<p><strong>Tiny undead, chaotic evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 19</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 22 (9d4)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 0 ft., fly 50 ft. (hover)</p>

